						               													<description>Travel around the city of Kobe and take the best photos to win the game!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Zoom in Kobe, players compete in a photo contest to try to take the best photos of the city. During the game, you take photos of its beautiful locations, the iconic structures found in Kobe, and...weathercocks, one of the symbols of Kobe!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of this board game for 2-6 players is to score the highest number of points to win the photography contest. When a player takes their eighth landmark photo, the game ends, then the photographer with the most points wins. Points can be scored by:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    Taking photographs of the landmarks selected by the judges, with bonus points awarded if the photos contain the relevant themes of the game (different themes will be revealed for each game)&amp;#10;    Taking photographs of the different buildings of the skyline of the city.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game contains 75 landmark cards with beautiful illustrations of locations of the city of Kobe. First time players learning the basic mechanisms of the game, or those who want a shorter play time can play with the Photography Starter Kit version.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
